Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}活在自己的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}活在自己梦想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这样的父亲我始终不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}甚至是憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}和我父亲一样
