Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}周围的人都说他是个心细的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不过他其实是个软弱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}只会逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}逃避家人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不断逃避的人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}像孩子一样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}母亲要和父亲离婚，我马上赞成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}因为母亲一直活在泪水里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}父亲虽然像是受了打击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}但那时却笑着说自己是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}最后却替我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}死了
